[emph]What is a notification?[/emph]

Notification tab allows you to send an email to the people related to the item, after saving it. No matter whether it
is a new item or it is being modified an existing one.


[emph]Who are the recipients of it?[/emph]

The recipients will be determined automatically by the module according a pre-defined criterion.
The idea is to send an email to the people that may be concerned about the creation or modification of the item, if it
is a Project, all people with at least Read access; if it is a Todo item, also the assigned user, etc.


[emph]What are its contents?[/emph]

Its contents are generally the description of the item, including Basic Data tab fields and exceptionally other 
important content.